credentials.json
*.pem
*.key
id_rsa*
id_dsa*
.aws/
.gnupg/
.netrc

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local Claude Code state — user-specific skills and permissions.
# `.claude/settings.local.json` carries the user's per-prompt approval
# history; `.claude/skills/` carries vendored Claude Code skills that
# are user-installed, NOT project deliverables (the project's own skill
# bundle lives at `skills/ia-pptx/`).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/skills/
.claude/settings.local.json

